properties.Name: RefineryProcessItem
properties.Description: Item(s) such as chemicals, material or other inventoried items consumed or produced by the Refinery Process during the associated period.

Columns.Name: RefineryProcessId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the refinery process.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.

Columns.Name: RefineryProcessItemRelationshipTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Refinery Process Item Relationship Type.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp of the associated refinery process - item relationship.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp of the associated refinery process - item relationship.

Columns.Name: RefineryProcessItemUnits
Columns.Description: The units of the item consumed/produced/wasted by the refinery process during the indicated period.

Columns.Name: UnitOfMeasureId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: RefineryProcessItemNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the refinery process item.
